Replication files for “Nowcasting in a Pandemic using Non-Parametric Mixed Frequency VARs” by F. Huber, G. Koop, L. Onorante, M. Pfarrhofer and J. Schreiner

Source-files:
“mfbart.R” contains the main function to estimate the MF-BAVART model. 
“aux_func.R” collects several auxiliary and helper functions needed for estimating the model.
“insample_script.R” shows how to use the MF-BAVART for insample analysis.
“simulation_script.R” contains the simulation study.
“data_script.R” transforms xls-files in “raw-data” for use of the functions.

“raw-data” contains raw xls-files of our dataset for all four countries.
